metadata.name: genesis
metadata.description:
progress is a continuous exploration of the process behind launching a long-form generative art collection or more curated short-form piece.

every time major changes are made to in-progress algorithms, a piece is posted on the divergence twitter account and made available for mint requests.

if a mint request is submitted, a 24 hour auction will be kicked off starting at .01eth. if it is not requested, that piece will be lost forever in the sands of time.

the genesis piece is a special case that will be listed on Foundation for a reserve of .05eth.
